<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Análisis de Competidores — Ricki Pollo | Mercado Rosticerias Puebla</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      background: #f8f9fb;
      color: #1a1a2e;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    /* HEADER */
    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2e 0%, #16213e 60%, #0f3460 100%);
      color: white;
      padding: 48px 40px 36px;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .header::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      bottom: -30px; left: 0; right: 0;
      height: 60px;
      background: #f8f9fb;
      clip-path: ellipse(55% 100% at 50% 100%);
    }
    .header-inner {
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: flex-start;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 16px;
    }
    .header h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: -0.5px;
      line-height: 1.2;
    }
    .header h1 span { color: #f39c12; }
    .header p { margin-top: 8px; opacity: 0.75; font-size: 0.95rem; }
    .header-meta { text-align: right; }
    .header-meta .date { font-size: 0.85rem; opacity: 0.65; }
    .powered {
      display: inline-block;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 4px 14px;
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      margin-top: 8px;
      letter-spacing: 0.3px;
    }
    .powered span { color: #f39c12; }

    /* CONTAINER */
    .container {
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 60px 24px 80px;
    }

    /* SECTION TITLE */
    .section-title {
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #1a1a2e;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
      padding-bottom: 12px;
      border-bottom: 3px solid #f39c12;
      display: inline-block;
    }

    /* COMPETITOR GRID */
    .competitors-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(480px, 1fr));
      gap: 32px;
      margin-bottom: 72px;
    }

    /* COMPETITOR CARD */
    .card {
      background: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 16px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(26,26,46,0.08), 0 1px 3px rgba(26,26,46,0.04);
      overflow: hidden;
      transition: box-shadow 0.2s;
    }
    .card:hover {
      box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(26,26,46,0.14), 0 2px 8px rgba(26,26,46,0.06);
    }

    .card-header {
      padding: 20px 24px 16px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f5;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 12px;
    }
    .card-title { font-size: 1.15rem; font-weight: 700; color: #1a1a2e; }
    .card-address { font-size: 0.82rem; color: #888; margin-top: 4px; }

    .rating-badge {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 5px;
      padding: 5px 12px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      white-space: nowrap;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .rating-green { background: #d4f5e3; color: #1a8c50; }
    .rating-yellow { background: #fef3cd; color: #9a6200; }
    .rating-red { background: #fde8e8; color: #c0392b; }

    /* MAP */
    .map-wrapper {
      position: relative;
      width: 100%;
      height: 220px;
      background: #eef0f5;
    }
    .map-wrapper iframe {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      border: none;
      display: block;
    }

    /* CARD BODY */
    .card-body { padding: 20px 24px; }

    .info-row {
      display: flex;
      gap: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      font-size: 0.87rem;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }
    .info-icon { font-size: 1rem; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 1px; }
    .info-label { font-weight: 600; color: #555; margin-right: 4px; }

    /* PLATFORMS */
    .platforms { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 6px; margin: 12px 0 16px; }
    .platform-badge {
      padding: 4px 12px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.3px;
    }
    .p-uber { background: #06C167; color: white; }
    .p-rappi { background: #FF441F; color: white; }
    .p-didi { background: #FF5C00; color: white; }
    .p-none { background: #e5e7eb; color: #6b7280; font-style: italic; font-weight: 500; }

    /* REVIEWS */
    .reviews { margin: 14px 0; }
    .review {
      padding: 10px 14px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      font-size: 0.83rem;
      line-height: 1.5;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .review-pos { background: #f0faf5; border-left: 3px solid #2ecc71; color: #1d5c38; }
    .review-neg { background: #fff5f5; border-left: 3px solid #e74c3c; color: #7b1e1e; }
    .review-neu { background: #f5f5f5; border-left: 3px solid #bbb; color: #555; }

    /* STRENGTHS/WEAKNESSES */
    .sw-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 10px; margin-top: 14px; }
    .sw-box { border-radius: 10px; padding: 12px 14px; font-size: 0.83rem; line-height: 1.5; }
    .sw-strong { background: #f0faf5; border: 1px solid #b6f0d0; }
    .sw-strong .sw-label { color: #1a8c50; font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.75rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px; margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .sw-weak { background: #fff5f5; border: 1px solid #f5c0c0; }
    .sw-weak .sw-label { color: #c0392b; font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.75rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px; margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .sw-box p { color: #444; }

    /* DIVIDER */
    .divider { height: 1px; background: #f0f0f5; margin: 16px 0; }

    /* OPPORTUNITIES SECTION */
    .opportunities { margin-top: 16px; }
    .opp-title {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: #1a1a2e;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .opp-subtitle { color: #666; margin-bottom: 32px; font-size: 0.95rem; }

    .opp-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(230px, 1fr)); gap: 20px; }
    .opp-card {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2e 0%, #0f3460 100%);
      color: white;
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 24px 20px;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .opp-card::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: -20px; right: -20px;
      width: 80px; height: 80px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: rgba(243,156,18,0.15);
    }
    .opp-num {
      font-size: 2rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: #f39c12;
      line-height: 1;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .opp-label {
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      color: #f39c12;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }
    .opp-card h3 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .opp-card p { font-size: 0.83rem; opacity: 0.8; line-height: 1.5; }

    /* FOOTER */
    .footer {
      background: #1a1a2e;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
      text-align: center;
      padding: 24px;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
    }
    .footer strong { color: #f39c12; }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .competitors-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .sw-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .header h1 { font-size: 1.5rem; }
      .opp-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<header class="header">
  <div class="header-inner">
    <div>
      <h1>Mercado de <span>Rosticerias</span><br>Puebla / Cholula</h1>
      <p>Análisis competitivo para <strong style="color:#fff">Ricki Pollo</strong> — 5 competidores identificados</p>
    </div>
    <div class="header-meta">
      <div class="date">📅 Marzo 2026</div>
      <div class="powered">Powered by <span>AgentX</span></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<div class="container">

  <div class="section-title">🐔 Competidores Directos</div>

  <div class="competitors-grid">

    <!-- 1. Pollo Feliz Zavaleta -->
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-header">
        <div>
          <div class="card-title">Pollo Feliz Zavaleta</div>
          <div class="card-address">📍 Calz. Zavaleta 98, Zavaleta, Puebla</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span class="rating-badge rating-yellow">⭐ 4.3 Google</span><br>
          <span class="rating-badge rating-green" style="margin-top:4px">⭐ 4.8 UE</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="map-wrapper">
        <iframe src="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Pollo+Feliz+Zavaleta+Calzada+Zavaleta+98+Puebla" loading="lazy" allowfullscreen referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"></iframe>
      </div>
      <div class="card-body">
        <div class="info-row"><span class="info-icon">🕐</span><span><span class="info-label">Horario:</span> Lun–Dom: 12:01 PM – 6:45 PM</span></div>
        <div class="info-row"><span class="info-icon">💰</span><span><span class="info-label">Precio:</span> No publicado oficialmente</span></div>
        <div class="platforms">
          <span class="platform-badge p-uber">Uber Eats</span>
          <span class="platform-badge p-rappi">Rappi</span>
        </div>
        <div class="divider"></div>
        <div class="reviews">
          <div class="review review-pos">🟢 "La sucursal de Zavaleta tiene un sazón tan similar al de mi padre. Esta sucursal me volvió fan de Pollo Feliz." — Brau</div>
          <div class="review review-neg">🔴 "Para mí ha bajado de calidad, faltan cosas y el servicio varía." — Sebahattin</div>
        </div>
        <div class="sw-grid">
          <div class="sw-box sw-strong">
            <div class="sw-label">✅ Fortaleza</div>
            <p>La sucursal más querida de Pollo Feliz en Puebla. Acepta tarjetas, estacionamiento.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="sw-box sw-weak">
            <div class="sw-label">⚠️ Debilidad</div>
            <p>Horario limitado, servicio lento en hora pico, sin barra de ensaladas.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 2. Pollo Feliz Cholula -->
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-header">
        <div>
          <div class="card-title">Pollo Feliz Cholula</div>
          <div class="card-address">📍 Calle 14 Ote 1, San Andrés Cholula, Pue.</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span class="rating-badge rating-green">⭐ 4.8 UE</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="map-wrapper">
        <iframe src="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Pollo+Feliz+Calle+14+Oriente+San+Andres+Cholula" loading="lazy" allowfullscreen referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"></iframe>
      </div>
      <div class="card-body">
        <div class="info-row"><span class="info-icon">🕐</span><span><span class="info-label">Horario:</span> Lun–Dom: 12:01 PM – 6:45 PM</span></div>
        <div class="info-row"><span class="info-icon">💰</span><span><span class="info-label">Precio:</span> No publicado</span></div>
        <div class="platforms">
          <span class="platform-badge p-uber">Uber Eats</span>
          <span class="platform-badge p-rappi">Rappi</span>
        </div>
        <div class="divider"></div>
        <div class="reviews">
          <div class="review review-pos">🟢 "Todo llegó excelente presentación, empaquetado, sabor. Gracias" — Juan H.</div>
          <div class="review review-pos">🟢 "Todo bien" — Karen C.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="sw-grid">
          <div class="sw-box sw-strong">
            <div class="sw-label">✅ Fortaleza</div>
            <p>Rating altísimo (4.8) con +2,000 reseñas. Única Pollo Feliz en Cholula.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="sw-box sw-weak">
            <div class="sw-label">⚠️ Debilidad</div>
            <p>Solo abre de mediodía en adelante.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 3. Sabornis -->
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-header">
        <div>
          <div class="card-title">Sabornis Pollos y Costillas Ahumadas</div>
          <div class="card-address">📍 Calz. Zavaleta 1953, Sta. Cruz Buenavista, Puebla</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span class="rating-badge rating-green">⭐ 4.7 UE</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="map-wrapper">
        <iframe src="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Sabornis+Pollos+Costillas+Calzada+Zavaleta+1953+Puebla" loading="lazy" allowfullscreen referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"></iframe>
      </div>
      <div class="card-body">
        <div class="info-row"><span class="info-icon">🕐</span><span><span class="info-label">Horario:</span> Lun–Dom: 10:00 AM – 6:30 PM</span></div>
        <div class="info-row"><span class="info-icon">💰</span><span><span class="info-label">Precio:</span> $335.80 MXN (pollo ahumado)</span></div>
        <div class="platforms">
          <span class="platform-badge p-uber">Uber Eats</span>
          <span class="platform-badge p-didi">DiDi Food</span>
          <span class="platform-badge p-rappi">Rappi</span>
        </div>
        <div class="divider"></div>
        <div class="reviews">
          <div class="review review-pos">🟢 "Muy buen sabor" — 96% aprobación en Uber Eats (455 reseñas del pollo ahumado)</div>
          <div class="review review-neg">🔴 "Algunas piezas estaban crudas, el pollo no se veía ni rico." — RestaurantGuru</div>
        </div>
        <div class="sw-grid">
          <div class="sw-box sw-strong">
            <div class="sw-label">✅ Fortaleza</div>
            <p>Tradición desde 1980. Producto diferenciado: pollo ahumado artesanal. Las 3 plataformas.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="sw-box sw-weak">
            <div class="sw-label">⚠️ Debilidad</div>
            <p>Precio más alto (~$335). No es rostizado tradicional a la leña.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 4. Rosticería Molinos -->
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-header">
        <div>
          <div class="card-title">Rosticería Molinos</div>
          <div class="card-address">📍 Calle 3 Norte 202, Centro, San Pedro Cholula</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span class="rating-badge rating-red">⭐ 3.1/5</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="map-wrapper">
        <iframe src="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Rosticeria+Molinos+Calle+3+Norte+202+San+Pedro+Cholula" loading="lazy" allowfullscreen referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"></iframe>
      </div>
      <div class="card-body">
        <div class="info-row"><span class="info-icon">🕐</span><span><span class="info-label">Horario:</span> Lun–Dom: 9:00 AM – 9:00 PM</span></div>
        <div class="info-row"><span class="info-icon">💰</span><span><span class="info-label">Precio:</span> ~$260 MXN (combo con papas + refresco)</span></div>
        <div class="platforms">
          <span class="platform-badge p-didi">DiDi Food</span>
        </div>
        <div class="divider"></div>
        <div class="reviews">
          <div class="review review-pos">🟢 "Riquísimos y muy buena atención, son los mejores de calidad y sabor." — Esther</div>
          <div class="review review-neg">🔴 "Pésimo pollo, vendiendo pollo en mal estado. A mi familia les dio infección estomacal." — Ernesto</div>
        </div>
        <div class="sw-grid">
          <div class="sw-box sw-strong">
            <div class="sw-label">✅ Fortaleza</div>
            <p>Horario más amplio (9AM–9PM). Local en el corazón de San Pedro Cholula.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="sw-box sw-weak">
            <div class="sw-label">⚠️ Debilidad</div>
            <p>Rating muy bajo (3.1). Reportes serios sobre higiene. Solo DiDi Food.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 5. Rosticería La Granja -->
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-header">
        <div>
          <div class="card-title">Rosticería La Granja</div>
          <div class="card-address">📍 Cholula de Rivadavia, Pue.</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span class="rating-badge rating-yellow">⭐ 7.6/10 FS</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="map-wrapper">
        <iframe src="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Rosticeria+La+Granja+Cholula+Puebla" loading="lazy" allowfullscreen referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"></iframe>
      </div>
      <div class="card-body">
        <div class="info-row"><span class="info-icon">🕐</span><span><span class="info-label">Horario:</span> Solo fines de semana: Sáb 2–7:30 PM | Dom 1:30–7:30 PM</span></div>
        <div class="info-row"><span class="info-icon">💰</span><span><span class="info-label">Precio:</span> No publicado (porciones muy generosas)</span></div>
        <div class="platforms">
          <span class="platform-badge p-none">Sin delivery</span>
        </div>
        <div class="divider"></div>
        <div class="reviews">
          <div class="review review-pos">🟢 "Quizá de entrada parece precio alto, pero son enormes. La salsa deliciosa. Parada obligada." — Jacob I.</div>
          <div class="review review-neg">🔴 "Solo en fines de semana 🙃" — cliente Foursquare</div>
        </div>
        <div class="sw-grid">
          <div class="sw-box sw-strong">
            <div class="sw-label">✅ Fortaleza</div>
            <p>Más de 60 años de tradición en Cholula. Porciones generosas. Institución local.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="sw-box sw-weak">
            <div class="sw-label">⚠️ Debilidad</div>
            <p>Solo sábados y domingos por la tarde. Sin delivery. Apenas 5-6 horas/semana.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>

  <!-- OPPORTUNITIES SECTION -->
  <div class="opportunities">
    <div class="opp-title">🚀 Oportunidades de Mercado para Ricki Pollo</div>
    <p class="opp-subtitle">Gaps identificados frente a la competencia directa en Puebla y Cholula</p>
    <div class="opp-grid">
      <div class="opp-card">
        <div class="opp-num">01</div>
        <div class="opp-label">Gap de Delivery</div>
        <h3>Mercado Digital Desatendido</h3>
        <p>La Granja opera sin apps y Molinos solo tiene DiDi Food. Amplia oportunidad en Uber Eats y Rappi sin competidores locales fuertes.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="opp-card">
        <div class="opp-num">02</div>
        <div class="opp-label">Horario Extendido</div>
        <h3>Abierto Cuando Otros Cierran</h3>
        <p>Ningún competidor abre consistentemente antes de las 10 AM ni más allá de las 9 PM. Capturar desayunos y cenas tardías.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="opp-card">
        <div class="opp-num">03</div>
        <div class="opp-label">Diferenciador Único</div>
        <h3>Leña de Encino</h3>
        <p>Solo Sabornis se diferencia con técnica (ahumado), pero nadie tiene "leña de encino" como Ricki Pollo. Sabor imposible de replicar industrialmente.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="opp-card">
        <div class="opp-num">04</div>
        <div class="opp-label">Precio Accesible</div>
        <h3>Sabor Superior, Mejor Precio</h3>
        <p>Sabornis cobra $335 sin ser a la leña. Ricki Pollo puede posicionarse con producto superior a precio más accesible y ganar la comparación directa.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>

<footer class="footer">
  <p>Reporte generado en Marzo 2026 · Datos de fuentes públicas (Google, Uber Eats, Rappi, Foursquare, RestaurantGuru) · <strong>Powered by AgentX</strong> — byagentx.com</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
